## nginx — Fluentbit

nginx escribe access logs en JSON al volumen `nginx_logs`. Fluentbit hace tail y los shipper a OpenSearch.

```
nginx access log (JSON) → /var/log/nginx/access.log (volumen nginx_logs)
  → Fluentbit tail + parser nginx_json
  → POST a streamerv2-nginx-YYYY.MM.DD
```

Config: `docker/fluentbit/fluent-bit.conf` + `docker/fluentbit/parsers.conf`

