## Infraestructura Docker

| Servicio | Imagen | Puerto |
|---|---|---|
| `opensearch` | `opensearchproject/opensearch:2.13.0` | `9200` |
| `opensearch-dashboards` | `opensearchproject/opensearch-dashboards:2.13.0` | `5601` |
| `fluentbit` | `fluent/fluent-bit:latest` | — |

Seguridad deshabilitada en ambos (`DISABLE_SECURITY_PLUGIN=true`). `single-node`. Volumen: `opensearch_data`.

